original_title: The Test of Fitness (The 2013 Reebok Crossfit Games)
overview: A documentary about creating the ultimate test of fitness, the CrossFit Games.  Nearly 12 years ago, CrossFit Founder and CEO Greg Glassman defined fitness. In 2007, the first test to find the fittest man and woman on Earth was born: the CrossFit Games.
title: The Test of Fitness (The 2013 Reebok Crossfit Games)
